latestPosts.caption:
The radiant grace upon her countenance
captivated every gaze, Myriad hearts surrendered,
painted in hues under her enchanting sway. Yet,
when you perceive her laughter through the lens
of my eye, Only then shall you fathom the ache,
eclipsing even that beguiling display. @agira.poetry
